  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 240ºC/ 220ºC (fan)/ gas 9</p><p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Deseed the<strong> peppers</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and roughly chop into bite-size pieces</p><p>Crush the <strong>garlic cloves</strong> open by squashing with the side of a knife and remove the skin</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
